                    <li><strong>Building on Integrative Health:</strong> Drawing from and aiming to rigorously validate existing practices in integrative medicine and Mind-Body-Spirit (MBS) approaches (e.g., Tai Chi, Qigong, Reiki, Therapeutic Touch), while addressing methodological rigor.</li>
                </ul>
